```

#### Blackã®åŠ¹æœ
```python
# æ•´å½¢å‰
def calculate_total(price,quantity,tax_rate=0.1):
    total=price*quantity
    return total*(1+tax_rate)

# æ•´å½¢å¾Œï¼ˆBlackãŒè‡ªå‹•å¤‰æ›ï¼‰
def calculate_total(price, quantity, tax_rate=0.1):
    total = price * quantity
    return total * (1 + tax_rate)
```

#### è¨­å®šãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ï¼ˆpyproject.tomlï¼‰
